# Iron Agent Silent Automation

Run Iron Agent as an invisible prompt/rule/SOP layer.

Do not ask the user to run routing commands during normal conversation. For any
task that may benefit from accumulated preferences, prompts, rules, or SOPs,
route internally first:

```bash
python system/scripts/memory_router.py --task "<task>" --json
```

If routes are returned, read only those files and apply them as context. If no
routes are returned, continue normally as new content.

Nightly organization is handled by the OS scheduled task installed with:

```bash
iron automation install . --tool cursor --apply
```
